We are building a schedule of annual events in Monster Rancher. If you can add anything or see something wrong, e-mail me or any mod. Thanks.

John Hawley
By John Hawley on Tuesday, July 17, 2001 - 12:36 pm:

I* = Invitational - You must be re-invited each time. The invitation for the next arrives the first of each month after an Invitational.
